`packages/app-providers/src/providers/github/api.ts:77` — the `ApiEndpoint` interface only allows `method: "GET" | "POST"`. No `PUT` endpoint exists for `PUT /repos/{owner}/{repo}/contents/{path}` (needed for memory commits).

